We, init innovation in traffic systems SE, are pleased that you are interested in our mobile app DeparturesLive. We take the protection of your privacy very seriously. For this reason, we always treat your data confidentially and in accordance with data protection laws (in particular the EU General Data Protection Regulation).
The sections below contain information on the extent to which we process your personal data, and for which purposes, when you decide to use our app.
1.    General information
We collect, utilize, or store ("process") your personal data in order to ensure the proper functioning of the services we offer you. Personal data means any information that can be used to identify a person, i.e. information that can be traced back to an individual. This includes names, addresses, e-mail addresses, and telephone numbers.
The controller responsible for data processing under Article 4 (7) GDPR is:
